nodes.bodyText:
You need to update LICENSE including

Versions of lang-mustache-client and parent-join-client
Add mapper-extras-client with license as we missed before
Add rank-eval-client with license as we missed before, both 6.3.2(es6 package) and 7.5.0(you updated)

Elasticsearch BV (Elasticsearch) 6.3.2, 7.5.0: https://www.elastic.co/products/elasticsearch , Apache 2.0

For multiple versions, should be like this.
